# install

## script

to install with a script,
  
  cd ~
  git clone https://github.com/ahdinosaur/dotfiles.git
  cd dotfiles/
  cp -r ./ ../
  cd ../
  rm -rf dotfiles

# cfengine

to install with cfengine,

  cf-sketch --install VCS::vcs_mirror
  cf-sketch --activate VCS::vcs_mirror --params https://raw.github.com/ahdinosaur/dotfiles/master/install.json
  cf-sketch --generate
  cf-agent -KI -f ~/.cfagent/inputs/cf-sketch-runfile.cf
